# LC25000 Histopathology Dataset Preprocessing Pipeline

This repository contains the standalone, production-grade data loader and data augmentation preprocessing module configured for multi-class lung and colon cancer histopathology classification workflows.

## 📁 Dataset Reference
The pipeline interfaces directly with the benchmark **[LC25000 Lung and Colon Cancer Histopathological Images Dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/andrewmvd/lung-and-colon-cancer-histopathological-images)**.

## ⚙️ Configuration Blueprint
* **Target Spatial Dimensions:** $300 \times 300 \times 3$ pixels
* **Intensity Scale:** Normalized to $[0, 1]$ intensity range
* **Stain-Invariant Augmentations:** Random rotations, spatial flips, zoom, shear distortions, and brightness perturbations
* **Data Split Topology:** **85% Training** data generator and **15% Validation** data generator split

